  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "<span class=\"name name-earth\">Uranium</span> is found primarily on worlds with a <span class=\"name name-commodity\">radioactive environment</span>. Typically found in large deposits and located with the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Analysis Visor</span>.<br>Common ferrite rocks may yield Uranium after inspection with an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Analysis Visor</span>. Can be <span class=\"name name-technology\">refined</span> from other terrain elements.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "<span class=\"name name-earth\">铀</span>主要出现在具有<span class=\"name name-commodity\">放射性环境</span>的世界里。通常可在大型矿床中找到，可使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析面甲</span>来定位。<br>使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析面甲</span>来检查普通铁氧体岩石，可能发现铀。可由其他岩层元素<span class=\"name name-technology\">精炼</span>得到。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-earth\">鈾</span>主要可見於<span class=\"name name-commodity\">輻射環境</span>的世界。常見於大型資源產地，並可用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析護目鏡</span>找到。<br>常見的鐵氧體岩石在使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析護目鏡</span>檢驗後可能會產出鈾。可從其他地形元素<span class=\"name name-technology\">精製</span>而成。"
  },
